org.netbeans.libs.git

Enum GitRepositoryState

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<GitRepositoryState>
      • org.netbeans.libs.git.GitRepositoryState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<GitRepositoryState>

    public enum GitRepositoryState
extends Enum<GitRepositoryState>
    Represents th state a repository is currently in. The state implies what git commands may be called on the repository and what should be the next steps to get the repository into a normal state.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants

      APPLY

      An unfinished merge.
      MERGING_RESOLVED
      A merge where all conflicts have been resolved.
      REBASING
      An unfinished rebase or am.
      SAFE
      A safe state for working normally
